<li><a href="http://gregegan.customer.netspace.net.au/FOUNDATIONS/01/found01.html" class="external text" title="http://gregegan.customer.netspace.net.au/FOUNDATIONS/01/found01.html" rel="nofollow">Greg Egan's <i>Foundations</i></a></li>
