<li><a href="http://www.black-holes.org/relativity1.html" class="external text" title="http://www.black-holes.org/relativity1.html" rel="nofollow">Caltech Relativity Tutorial</a> A basic introduction to concepts of Special and General Relativity, requiring only a knowledge of basic geometry.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.phys.unsw.edu.au/einsteinlight/" class="external text" title="http://www.phys.unsw.edu.au/einsteinlight/" rel="nofollow">Special Relativity in film clips and animations</a> from the University of New South Wales.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.relativitycalculator.com/" class="external text" title="http://www.relativitycalculator.com/" rel="nofollow">Relativity Calculator - Learn Special Relativity Mathematics</a> Mathematics of special relativity presented in as simple and comprehensive manner possible within philosophical and historical contexts.</li>
<li><a href="http://insti.physics.sunysb.edu/~siegel/sr.html" class="external text" title="http://insti.physics.sunysb.edu/~siegel/sr.html" rel="nofollow">Special relativity made stupid ☺</a>.</li>
